text: Bryan Reynolds (born June 28, 2001) is an American soccer player who currently plays for FC Dallas in Major League Soccer. == Career == After playing with the FC Dallas academy, Reynolds became the club's youngest ever Homegrown Player on November 23, 2016 when he signed a contract with the first-team. == References == == External links == * * * Category:2001 births Category:Living people Category:American soccer players Category:Association football forwards Category:FC Dallas players Category:North Texas SC players Category:Soccer players from Texas Category:Sportspeople from Fort Worth, Texas Category:USL League One players Category:Major League Soccer players Category:Homegrown Players (MLS)
